msgid ""
"Young and brash, Fighters fight with a sword, and are vulnerable to attack "
"from enemies. However they have the potential to become great warriors one "
"day."
msgstr ""
"年轻性急的战士使用剑，易受敌人攻击。然而他们有可能某一天成为伟大的勇士。"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Lord.cfg:3
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Lord.cfg:92
#: data/tutorial/units/Lord.cfg:3 data/tutorial/units/Lord.cfg:91
msgid "Lord"
msgstr "君主"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Lord.cfg:28
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Lord.cfg:117
#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Noble_Lord.cfg:41
#: data/tutorial/units/Lord.cfg:28 data/tutorial/units/Lord.cfg:116
msgid ""
"The noble leaders of many troops, Lords are especially strong in melee "
"combat, and also possess skill with the bow. Like Commanders, Lords possess "
"leadership skills, and improve the fighting ability of all adjacent lower-"
"level units."
msgstr ""
"许多军队的高级领袖，君主在近战中特别强而有力，并有弓技能，像指挥官一样，君主"
"拥有领导技能，并让相邻的低级单位改进战斗能力。"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Princess.cfg:3
msgid "female^Princess"
msgstr "公主"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Princess.cfg:28
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Princess.cfg:77
msgid ""
"A noble by birth, the Princess has learnt swordplay with the greatest "
"generals and battle tactics with the greatest sages, making her both a great "
"combatant and leader. The units of lower level around the Princess will "
"fight better due to her presence. The Princess is also nimble and dextrous, "
"having skills like that of a thief."
msgstr ""
"天生贵族，公主与最伟大的将军学习战术，使得他们成为高超的战斗者和领袖。公主相"
"邻的低级单位在她的领导下能更好的战斗。公主也十分灵活和敏捷，有着如小偷般的技"
"能。"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Princess.cfg:53
msgid "Princess"
msgstr "公主"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Sea_Orc.cfg:3
msgid "Sea Orc"
msgstr "海洋兽"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Sea_Orc.cfg:23
msgid ""
"While often viewed as inferior to their land loving counterparts, Sea Orcs "
"represent a great leap for all goblinoids as they have adapted to aquatic "
"environments. With their curved swords they are competent fighters, although "
"their lack of a ranged attack and poor defence on land do represent "
"strategic weaknesses."
msgstr ""
"尽管通常认为比陆地上的同类低级。海洋兽是goblinoids人的领袖正如他们不得不适应"
"水中的环境。有着弯曲的剑，使得他们能胜任战士这一职业，虽然他们缺乏有效的远程"
"攻击和在陆地上疏于防御，表现出他们战略上的弱势。"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Sleeping_Gryphon.cfg:3
msgid "Sleeping Gryphon"
msgstr "沉睡狮鹫"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Sleeping_Gryphon.cfg:16
msgid "Shhhh! The Gryphon is sleeping! You'd better not wake it up!"
msgstr "嘘！狮鹫在睡觉！最好别吵醒他们！"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Youth.cfg:3
#: data/tutorial/units/Youth.cfg:3
msgid "Youth"
msgstr "青卫队"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Youth.cfg:23
#: data/tutorial/units/Youth.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Today almost a boy, by his devotion to the crown he is seeking to become a "
"Lord -- to join the elite of human fighters."
msgstr ""
"今天几乎是个孩子，为了能有一天成为君主而开始争夺王权之路 － 加入人类战士的精"
"英部队。"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Youth.cfg:26
#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Noble_Youth.cfg:29
#: data/tutorial/units/Youth.cfg:26
msgid "training sword"
msgstr "训练剑术"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Leader.cfg:3
msgid "Orcish Leader"
msgstr "兽人领袖"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Leader.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Orcish Leaders are the chiefs of their tribe. They make the important "
"decisions and lead their people into battle. They carry a bow out of "
"necessity, but are much more skilled with the sword; all in all, they are "
"powerful fighters. Their natural leadership skills make them very precious "
"in battle: if the Leader is lost, so is the battle."
msgstr ""
"兽人领袖是他们部族的领导。他们作出重大决议并带领族人战斗。他们虽然会携带弓，"
"但却有着强力的剑术技能：总而言之，他们是强力的战士，他们天生的领导技能使得他"
"们在战争中很珍贵：如果领袖死亡，战斗也一样。"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Ruler.cfg:3
msgid "Orcish Ruler"
msgstr "兽人统治者"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Ruler.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Orcish Rulers are the chiefs of their tribe. They make the important "
"decisions and lead their people into battle. They carry a bow out of "
"necessity, but are much more skilled with the sword; all in all, they are "
"powerful fighters. Their natural leadership skills make them very precious "
"in battle: if the Ruler is lost, so is the battle."
msgstr ""
"兽人统治者是他们部族的领袖。他们作出重大决议并带领族人战斗。他们虽然会携带"
"弓，但却有着强力的剑术技能：总而言之，他们是强力的战士，他们天生的领导技能使"
"得他们在战争中很珍贵：如果领袖死亡，战斗也一样。"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Shaman.cfg:3
msgid "Orcish Shaman"
msgstr "兽人萨满法师"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Shaman.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Orcish Shamans are the guardians of orcish magic. Respected among orcish "
"tribes, they form the Orcish Council, which makes important decisions for "
"the whole Orcish community and arbitrates the many conflicts that arise "
"between tribes of this argumentative race. Although physically weak (for "
"Orcs), Orcish Shamans are good spell casters and can curse their enemies, "
"draining their life."
msgstr ""
"兽人萨满法师是兽人魔法力量的保护者。受族人尊敬，他们组成兽人议会，为整个兽人"
"社区作重大决议，并为兽人族内的许多事情作判决。虽然身体虚弱 (相对兽人来说) 兽"
"人萨满是魔法施放高手，并能诅咒敌人，耗尽他们的生命。"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Shaman.cfg:48
#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Shaman.cfg:121
#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Shaman.cfg:194
#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Vampire_Lady.cfg:43
msgid "curse"
msgstr "诅咒"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Shaman.cfg:76
msgid "Novice Orcish Shaman"
msgstr "新手兽人萨满"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Shaman.cfg:99
msgid ""
"Orcish Shamans are the guardians of orcish magic. Respected among orcish "
"tribes, they form the Orcish Council, which makes important decisions for "
"the whole Orcish community and arbitrates the many conflicts that arise "
"between tribes of this argumentative race. Although physically weak (for "
"Orcs), Orcish Shamans are good spell casters and can curse their enemies, "
"draining their life. Novice Shamans are still young and vigorous, but their "
"spell-casting ability still needs improvement."
msgstr ""
"兽人萨满法师是兽人魔法力量的保护者。受族人尊敬，他们组成兽人议会，为整个兽人"
"社区作重大决议，并为兽人族内的许多事情作判决。虽然身体虚弱 (相对兽人来说) 兽"
"人萨满是魔法施放高手，并能诅咒敌人，耗尽他们的生命。选手萨满仍然年轻且精力充"
"沛，但他们施放魔法的能力仍需改进。"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Shaman.cfg:149
msgid "Old Orcish Shaman"
msgstr "萨满法师长老"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Shaman.cfg:172
msgid ""
"Orcish Shamans are the guardians of orcish magic. Respected among orcish "
"tribes, they form the Orcish Council, which makes important decisions for "
"the whole Orcish community and arbitrates the many conflicts that arise "
"between tribes of this argumentative race. Although physically weak (for "
"Orcs), Orcish Shamans are good spell casters and can curse their enemies, "
"draining their life. Old Orcish Shamans are shamans that have mastered "
"magic, although their physical strength has declined with age."
msgstr ""
"兽人萨满法师是兽人魔法力量的保护者。受族人尊敬，他们组成兽人议会，为整个兽人"
"社区作重大决议，并为兽人族内的许多事情作判决。虽然身体虚弱 (相对兽人来说) 兽"
"人萨满是魔法施放高手，并能诅咒敌人，耗尽他们的生命。兽人法师长老是魔法大师，"
"即使他们的身体随着岁月的消逝而变得更虚弱。"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Sovereign.cfg:3
msgid "Orcish Sovereign"
msgstr "兽人君主"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Orcish_Sovereign.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Orcish Sovereigns are the chiefs of their tribe. They make the important "
"decisions and lead their people into battle. They carry a bow out of "
"necessity, but are much more skilled with the sword; all in all, they are "
"powerful fighters. Their natural leadership skills make them very precious "
"in battle: if the Sovereign is lost, so is the battle."
msgstr ""
"兽人君主是他们部族的领导。他们作出重大决议并带领族人战斗。他们虽然会携带弓，"
"但却有着强力的剑术技能：总而言之，他们是强力的战士，他们天生的领导技能使得他"
"们在战争中很珍贵：如果领袖死亡，战斗也一样。"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Watch_Tower.cfg:3
msgid "Watch Tower"
msgstr "观察塔"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Watch_Tower.cfg:16
msgid ""
"Watch Towers are good places from which to spot enemies and then shoot "
"miscellaneous items at them with ballistas."
msgstr "观察塔是个监视敌人的好地方，并能使用多种物品进行投石攻击。"

#: data/campaigns/Son_Of_The_Black_Eye/units/Watch_Tower.cfg:19
#: data/units/Pirate_Galleon.cfg:18 data/units/Transport_Galleon.cfg:18
msgid "ballista"
msgstr "投石器"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Dark_Spirit.cfg:3
msgid "Dark Spirit"
msgstr "黑暗灵魂"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Dark_Spirit.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Dark Spirits are messengers and bearers of tidings from the realm of the "
"dead, and a force of dread in this world. Happily, they have rarely been "
"seen in Wesnoth."
msgstr ""
"黑暗灵魂是死亡世界来的送信人，并有着恐怖的力量。幸运的是，他们在韦诺之地并不"
"常见。"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Dark_Spirit.cfg:38
#: data/units/Spectre.cfg:53 data/units/Wraith.cfg:29
msgid "baneblade"
msgstr "涂毒剑"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Dark_Spirit.cfg:57
#: data/units/Ghost.cfg:44 data/units/Spectre.cfg:72 data/units/Wraith.cfg:48
msgid "wail"
msgstr "哀嚎"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Deathmaster.cfg:3
msgid "Deathmaster"
msgstr "死亡大师"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Deathmaster.cfg:23
msgid ""
"His wanderings on a dark path have given him power normally not granted to "
"mortals, but with a terrible cost: the undead that he gave his soul to are "
"gradually claiming his mortal shell too, and with time, he will be a true "
"undead and a terror to all that lives."
msgstr ""
"他们徘徊在黑暗之路上，给予了超越人类的能力，但也要付出极大的代价：他将出卖他"
"们体内的灵魂，随着时间的流逝，他们的余生将成为真正的不死族。"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Deathmaster.cfg:61
#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Demilich.cfg:57
#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Dread_Lich.cfg:46
#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Initiate.cfg:43
#: data/units/Ancient_Lich.cfg:69 data/units/Lich.cfg:49
msgid "magic"
msgstr "魔法"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Demilich.cfg:3
msgid "Demilich"
msgstr "邪恶巫妖"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Demilich.cfg:27
msgid ""
"After too much time dabbling with forbidden magics and dark arts, these magi "
"have begun to pay a heavy price. Demiliches have started losing their "
"bodies, becoming undead themselves. With time, they may become fully undead, "
"and feared by all alike."
msgstr ""
"在使用足够的被禁止魔法和黑暗魔法后，这些魔法师将付出巨大的代价。他们开始失去"
"他们的身体，慢慢成为不死族。随着时间的流逝，他们将成为真正的不死族并被其他人"
"所惧怕。"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Demilich.cfg:42
#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Dread_Lich.cfg:31
#: data/units/Ancient_Lich.cfg:54 data/units/Ghost.cfg:29
#: data/units/Lich.cfg:34
msgid "touch"
msgstr "触碰"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Dread_Lich.cfg:3
msgid "Dread Lich"
msgstr "恐惧巫妖"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Dread_Lich.cfg:28
msgid ""
"At long last, Ha'atel has paid the ultimate sacrifice for the dark arts into "
"which he has delved, and has, himself, entered into undeath. At the apex of "
"his power, he has become a lich, a waking embodiment of dread. He has, "
"beyond any doubt, passed the point of no return, and his power and "
"immortality will have to provide consolation for what he has lost in his "
"quest to achieve them."
msgstr ""
"在远久的过去，Ha'atel为了追求黑暗能量而献出了终极祭品，使得他成为不死族。在能"
"力的顶峰，他成为了巫妖，一个活着且具体化的恐惧力量。超越了一切疑虑，走进了不"
"归路，他的能力和不朽是对他所失去的回报。"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Initiate.cfg:3
msgid "Initiate"
msgstr "传授者"

#: data/campaigns/The_Dark_Hordes/units/Initiate.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Dabbling in the Death Magic, this young Ha'atel's lust for power has "
"weakened him to the point where he is too weak to attack in regular combat."
msgstr ""
"专注于死亡魔法，这些年轻的Ha'atel追求力量而变得虚弱，使得他们在普通战斗中容易"
"被击中。"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Fire_Dragon.cfg:3
msgid "Fire Dragon"
msgstr "火龙"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Fire_Dragon.cfg:26
msgid ""
"A fire dragon is an ancient and horrifying being that normally lives only in "
"hushed rumor and fantastic stories. It is normal for centuries to pass "
"without a dragon being seen in Wesnoth, and usually it is only as a shadowy "
"form flying in the distance. Legends are very specific about the ravages of "
"fire dragons: hideously swift in flight, leathery wings spread over one "
"hundred feet in width, they swoop in and blast their prey with inferno jets "
"of flame. Anything escaping the dragon's fire breath must beware its "
"ferocious bite and crushing tail. Fire dragons are cunning and cruel and "
"often take underlings whom they lead to victory."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Fire_Dragon.cfg:29
msgid "bite"
msgstr "咬击"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Fire_Dragon.cfg:49
msgid "tail"
msgstr "尾击"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Fire_Dragon.cfg:70
#: data/units/Drake_Blademaster.cfg:98 data/units/Drake_Burner.cfg:88
#: data/units/Drake_Fighter.cfg:101 data/units/Drake_Fire.cfg:94
#: data/units/Drake_Flameheart.cfg:109 data/units/Drake_Flare.cfg:103
#: data/units/Drake_Glider.cfg:103 data/units/Drake_Hurricane.cfg:107
#: data/units/Drake_Inferno.cfg:95 data/units/Drake_Sky.cfg:108
#: data/units/Drake_Warrior.cfg:102
msgid "fire breath"
msgstr "火息术"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Fire_Dragon.cfg:73
#: data/units/Elvish_Marksman.cfg:85 data/units/Elvish_Sharpshooter.cfg:85
msgid "marksman"
msgstr "神射手"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Fireball.cfg:4
msgid "Fireball"
msgstr "火球"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Fireball.cfg:24
msgid ""
"A Fireball. This is not to be used for anything else than a 'Move_Unit_Fake'!"
msgstr "火球并不常用于‘伪装移动单位’等。"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Noble_Commander.cfg:3
msgid "Noble Commander"
msgstr "高阶指挥官"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Noble_Commander.cfg:40
msgid ""
"The rank of a noble Commander is held by those who lead battle groups into "
"combat. Possessing leadership skills, they give lower-level units in "
"adjacent hexes improved performance in combat. Commanders are best skilled "
"with the sword, although they also carry a bow to use when necessary. If the "
"Commander is lost, so is the battle."
msgstr ""
"高阶指挥官的等级使得他们在战斗中能组织有效的攻击。拥有领导技能，他们让相邻的"
"低级单位改进攻击能力。指挥官善于使用剑，必须时他们会用弓，如果失去指挥官，战"
"争也将失败。"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Noble_Fighter.cfg:3
msgid "Noble Fighter"
msgstr "高价战士"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Noble_Fighter.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Young and brash, Fighters fight with a sword, and are vulnerable to ranged "
"attacks from enemies. However they have the potential to become great "
"Commanders one day."
msgstr ""
"年轻而高傲，战士用剑作战，并易受远程攻击。然而他们有成为伟大指挥官的潜能。"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Noble_Lord.cfg:3
msgid "Noble Lord"
msgstr "高阶君主"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Noble_Youth.cfg:3
msgid "Noble Youth"
msgstr "高阶青卫队"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Noble_Youth.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Today he is a young man, by his devotion to the crown he is seeking to "
"become a Lord -- to join the elite of humanity."
msgstr ""
"今天他们是年轻人，但作为王位继承人有一天能成为君主 － 成为人类精英中的一员。"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Outlaw_Princess.cfg:4
msgid "female^Outlaw Princess"
msgstr "亡命之徒公主"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Outlaw_Princess.cfg:23
msgid ""
"A noble by birth, the Outlaw Princess has learnt swordplay with the greatest "
"generals, but she is the product of a failed aristocracy who has opted for "
"the life of an Outlaw. She dreams of founding her own Queendom with the "
"plunder she finds on the road."
msgstr ""
"天生贵族，她们和最伟大的将军一起联系剑术，但是确实那些投向亡命之徒的贵族的产"
"物。她们梦想着通过抢得的赃物来达到女王之路。"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Outlaw_Princess.cfg:80
#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Outlaw_Queen.cfg:82
#: data/units/Footpad.cfg:46 data/units/Outlaw.cfg:47
#: data/units/Troll_Rocklobber.cfg:52
msgid "sling"
msgstr "投石器"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Outlaw_Queen.cfg:3
msgid "female^Outlaw Queen"
msgstr "亡命之徒女王"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Outlaw_Queen.cfg:26
msgid ""
"A noble by birth, the Outlaw Queen has learnt swordplay with the greatest "
"generals and battle tactics with the greatest sages, making her both a great "
"combatant and leader. However, she is the product of a failed aristocracy "
"who has opted for the life of an Outlaw. She dreams of founding her own "
"Queendom with the plunder she finds on the road, and she is ever so close to "
"that goal."
msgstr ""
"天生贵族，她们和最伟大的将军一起练习剑术，但是确实那些投向亡命之徒的贵族的产"
"物。她们梦想着通过抢得的赃物来达到女王之路，并已经非常接近目标。"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Vampire_Lady.cfg:3
msgid "female^Vampire Lady"
msgstr "吸血贵妇"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Vampire_Lady.cfg:24
msgid ""
"Cold and beautiful, she maintains her eternal youthful appearance drinking "
"the blood of the living."
msgstr "冷艳，他们通过吸血来维持那永远年轻的面容。"

#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/units/Vampire_Lady.cfg:27
msgid "blood kiss"
msgstr "血之吻"

