#: data/tips.cfg:1
msgid ""
"Lawful units fight better at day, and chaotic units fight better at night. "
"Neutral units are unaffected by day and night."
msgstr ""
"善良单位在白天更善于战斗，混乱单位在晚上更善于战斗，中立单位不受时间的影响。"

#: data/tips.cfg:2
msgid ""
"In a campaign, you can use veteran units from previous scenarios by using "
"the 'recall' option."
msgstr "在战役中，你能使用上个剧本中战斗过有经验的单位。‘召回’选项。"

#: data/tips.cfg:3
msgid ""
"There are six types of attacks: pierce, blade, impact, fire, cold, and holy. "
"Different units have weaknesses against different types of attacks. Right-"
"click on a unit, and then select 'Unit Description', and then click "
"'Resistance' to see how much resistance a unit has against different attack "
"types."
msgstr ""
"有六种攻击方式：刺，砍，冲击，火，冰，和神圣。不同的单位对不同的攻击有不同的"
"反应。右击单位，再选择‘单位描述’，然后点选‘抗性’来查看一个单位对不同攻击的抵"
"抗力。"

#: data/tips.cfg:4
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The terrain your units are occupying determines the chance your opponents "
"have of hitting them in battle. The defensive rating for the currently "
"selected unit in the currently selected terrain is displayed in the top "
"right corner of the screen."
msgstr ""
"你的单位所处的地形决定了敌对方对你攻击造成伤害的几率。所选定单位所在地形对防"
"御的影响会在屏幕右上角显示。"

#: data/tips.cfg:5
msgid ""
"Poisoned units lose 8 hitpoints every turn, but they will not die from "
"poison: poison will never reduce them below 1 hitpoint. Poisoned units can "
"be cured by moving them to a village, or placing them next to a unit with "
"the 'cure' ability."
msgstr ""
"中毒的单位每回合损失8hp，但不会中毒而死。毒素影响不会使生命降到1hp以下。中毒"
"的单位可以通过移动到村庄或有‘治愈’能力的单位旁来治愈中毒影响。"

#: data/tips.cfg:6
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can use units from a previous scenario by selecting 'Recall' in the game "
"menu. By recalling the same units over and over, you can build up a powerful "
"and experienced army."
msgstr ""
"你可以通过选择在游戏菜单中的‘召回’选项来使用上个剧本中的单位。通过不停的召回"
"单位，可以让你建立一个强力和经验值丰富的军队。"

#: data/tips.cfg:7
msgid ""
"Units have a Zone of Control in each of the hexes next to them. If a unit "
"moves into an enemy's Zone of Control, it may not move any further that "
"turn. Level 0 units are too frail to control a zone; and skirmisher units "
"are skilled enough to ignore these zones."
msgstr ""
"在每个单位旁的格子都是各自的可控制区域。如果单位移动到敌人的可控制区域，它将"
"在本回合不能再移动。0级单位太脆弱而没有可控制区域，刺客则有技能来忽略这些区"
"域。"

#: data/tips.cfg:8
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The chance to hit a unit usually depends on how well that unit can defend "
"itself in the terrain it is standing in, however magical attacks have a 70% "
"chance to hit both when attacking and defending. Marksman attacks have at "
"least 60% chance to hit when attacking."
msgstr ""
"击中单位的几率依赖于这个单位在所处位置的防御力。然而魔法师攻击和防御时都有70%"
"的攻击几率，神枪手攻击是至少有60%的攻击几率。"

#: data/tips.cfg:9
msgid ""
"Units stationed in villages heal 8 hitpoints at the beginning of their turn."
msgstr "安置在村庄的单位每回合开始前可以恢复8hp。"

#: data/tips.cfg:10
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Units rest if they do not move or attack during their turn.  They will "
"recover 2 hitpoints at the beginning of their next turn."
msgstr "单位在本回合休息，不移动或攻击，能下回合开始前恢复2hp。"

#: data/tips.cfg:11
msgid ""
"Most foot units defend better in villages and castles than in most other "
"terrain, while most mounted units don't get any defensive advantage in "
"villages and castles."
msgstr ""
"大多数步兵单位在村庄和城堡中的防御要好于在其它地形，而大多数负重单位在城堡和"
"村庄中则不会有防御奖励。"

#: data/tips.cfg:12
msgid ""
"Horse based units are generally resistant to attacks with bladed or impact "
"weapons, but are vulnerable to attacks with piercing weapons, including bows "
"and spears."
msgstr ""
"骑兵单位通常能抵御砍或冲击武器，但却易受穿刺武器攻击，包括弓和长柄武器。"

#: data/tips.cfg:13
msgid ""
"Inflicting the killing blow on an enemy unit is the best way to gain "
"experience. Units killing an enemy will gain 8 experience for every level of "
"the unit they kill."
msgstr "杀敌是最好获得经验值的方式。单位杀敌会获得8xp每敌人等级。"

#: data/tips.cfg:14
msgid ""
"Elvish units move and fight very well in forest. Dwarvish units move and "
"fight very well in hills and mountains."
msgstr "精灵单位在森林中善于移动和战斗。矮人单位在丘陵和山脉中善于移动和战斗。"

#: data/tips.cfg:15
msgid ""
"Patience is often key. Rather than attacking in bad conditions, or with few "
"troops, wait for better conditions and then attack."
msgstr "耐性是处在坏情况时的关键，或有少数部队是，等待好时机再进行攻击。"

#: data/tips.cfg:16
msgid ""
"If you are attacked from several directions, it may be a good idea to send "
"expendable units in some directions to delay enemy units."
msgstr "如果你多面受敌，最好的方式是让可消耗的单位去拖延敌人单位。"

#: data/tips.cfg:17
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Do not be afraid to retreat and regroup; it is often the key to victory."
msgstr "别担心撤退或重组，通常是胜利的关键。"

#: data/tips.cfg:18
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In most campaigns you will receive a gold bonus for finishing early, "
"depending on the number of villages on the map and the number of turns you "
"finish early. You will always earn more gold this way than through capturing "
"villages and waiting for turns to run out."
msgstr ""
"在多数战役中，提前完成会获得金币奖励。根据地图上占领村庄的数量和提早结束的回"
"合数，会比占领多余的村庄并等待所有回合结束获得更多的金币。"

#: data/tips.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Your leader can recruit or recall units from any keep inside a castle, not "
"just the keep they start on. You can capture a keep from an enemy and "
"recruit from there. Also, some of your allies may be willing to make room "
"for you on their keep so you can recruit there."
msgstr ""
"你的领袖可以从城堡要塞中征募或召回单位，不仅仅是启始要塞。你可以征服敌人领"
"袖，并从那里征募单位。有些盟友在他们的要塞也有足够的空间让你征兵。"

#: data/tips.cfg:20
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Skeletons are resistant to piercing and bladed attacks but vulnerable to "
"impact, fire, and holy attacks."
msgstr "骷髅人对刺和砍有抗性，但却易受冲击，火和神圣伤害。"

#: data/tips.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Units with leadership ability make lower level adjacent units on the same "
"side fight better."
msgstr "有领导能力的单位会让相邻同一阵营的低级单位获得更好的攻击。"

#: data/tips.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Generally avoid moving next to an unoccupied village. An enemy unit may move "
"onto the village and attack you, while enjoying the defense and healing of "
"the village."
msgstr ""
"通常为了防止你进入一个未占领的村庄，一个敌人单位会移向村庄并攻击里，这是就可"
"以享受村庄带给你的防御和治疗优势了。"

#: data/tips.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Holding the mouse cursor on an ability or trait shows a description of that "
"ability or trait."
msgstr "当把鼠标放到能力或特质上时，会有一个详细的描述。"

#: data/tips.cfg:24
msgid "Use lines of units to screen injured units to let them recover."
msgstr "用单位掩护那些受伤害的单位，让他们恢复。"

#: data/tips.cfg:25
msgid "Read the hotkeys list in the preferences menu."
msgstr "在参数设置菜单你查看快捷键列表。"

#: data/tips.cfg:26
msgid ""
"If you move a unit, but don't attack or discover any additional information, "
"you can undo your move by pressing 'u'."
msgstr "如果你移动单位，但不攻击或发现一些附加信息，你可以看‘u’来撤销移动。"

#: data/tips.cfg:27
msgid ""
"You can see how far enemy units can move by moving the mouse cursor over "
"them."
msgstr "你能通过移动鼠标到敌人单位上面来查看敌人单位可以移动的最大距离。"

#: data/tips.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Use healers to support your attacks - they will win you battles without "
"needing to attack anything themselves."
msgstr "用治疗者来支持你的攻击 － 他们不需要任何攻击和你一起赢得战斗。"

#: data/tips.cfg:29
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The 'slow' attack ability makes enemy units move slower, but it also halves "
"the damage they do on all attacks."
msgstr ""
"‘慢速’攻击技能会让敌人单位移动减速，也能移出他们的可控制区域，并允许受伤单位"
"逃脱或帮助你逃避敌人单位。"

#: data/tips.cfg:30
msgid "Holy attacks are very powerful against undead."
msgstr "神圣攻击会对不死生物造成强力伤害。"

#: data/tips.cfg:31
msgid ""
"Units are healed when they advance a level. Used wisely, this can turn a "
"fight."
msgstr "单位升级时都会被治疗。精明的使用，会扭转战局。"

#: data/tips.cfg:32
msgid ""
"Charging units are best used against enemies they can kill with a single "
"blow."
msgstr "补充单位是最好的攻击敌人方式，他们能一回合内杀敌。"

#: data/tips.cfg:33
msgid ""
"Units can gain After Maximum Level Advancements (AMLA's), which usually "
"increase the unit's maximum hitpoints by 3. Gaining an AMLA becomes "
"progressively harder for each AMLA the unit receives, however. Thus, it is "
"often more useful to try to advance your lower level units."
msgstr ""

